                </h3>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
                  <div class="space-y-2">
                    <a href="#what-is-ai-document-management" class="block text-gray-300 hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300">• What is AI Document Management?</a>
                    <a href="#core-capabilities" class="block text-gray-300 hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300">• Core AI Capabilities</a>
                    <a href="#benefits-roi" class="block text-gray-300 hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300">• Benefits & ROI Analysis</a>
