    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <section class="py-8 bg-black">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <!-- Comprehensive Introduction -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 id="what-is-ai-document-management" class="text-3xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-8">What is an AI Document Management System?</h2>
              
              <div class="mb-8">
                <!-- Image 1: AI Technology - Right positioned, medium size -->
                <div class="float-right ml-6 mb-4 w-56" style="float: right; margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; width: 14rem; max-width: 14rem;">
                  <div style="position: relative; z-index: 999; background: #000; padding: 0; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
                    <img 
                      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677442136019-21780ecad995?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2032&q=80" 
                      alt="AI and machine learning technology for document management" 
                      class="w-full h-44 object-cover shadow-lg"
                      style="opacity: 1 !important; filter: none !important; background: #000 !important; display: block; position: relative; z-index: 1000;"
                    />
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
                  An <strong class="text-primary">AI document management system</strong> is an intelligent software platform that leverages artificial intelligence, machine learning, and natural language processing to automatically capture, classify, organize, and retrieve business documents. Unlike traditional document management software that relies on manual filing and keyword searches, AI-powered systems understand document content, context, and relationships to provide intelligent document organization and retrieval capabilities.
                </p>
                
                <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
                  Modern organizations generate and process millions of documents annually – from contracts and invoices to research reports and compliance documentation. Research from IDC shows that enterprises spend over <strong class="text-primary">$12,000 per knowledge worker annually</strong> on document-related activities, yet 90% of business information remains unstructured and difficult to access when needed.
                </p>
                
                <div class="bg-primary border-l-4 border-primary p-6 rounded-r-xl mb-6">
                  <h3 class="font-orbitron font-bold text-black mb-3">The Evolution of Document Management Technology</h3>
                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                    <div class="bg-black p-3 rounded">
                      <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2 text-sm">Traditional Systems</h4>
                      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Manual filing, folder hierarchies, basic keyword search</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-black p-3 rounded">
                      <h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2 text-sm">Digital Systems</h4>
                      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Electronic storage, metadata tagging, workflow automation</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-black p-3 rounded">
                      <h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2 text-sm">AI-Powered Systems</h4>
                      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Intelligent classification, semantic search, predictive organization</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed">
                  <strong class="text-primary">Intelligent document management systems</strong> represent the next generation of enterprise content management, combining advanced AI capabilities with traditional document storage to create systems that learn, adapt, and improve over time. These platforms typically achieve <strong class="text-primary">85-95% automation rates</strong> for document processing tasks while maintaining <strong class="text-primary">99%+ accuracy</strong> in classification and retrieval operations.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Key Features Section -->
            <div class="mb-12">
              <h2 id="core-capabilities" class="text-3xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-8">Core AI Document Management Capabilities</h2>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="glass-morphism p-6 rounded-xl">
                  <div class="bg-primary/20 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
