                  <h3 class="text-xl font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-3">AI-Powered Document Retrieval</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Advanced RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) technology enables semantic search, contextual understanding, and intelligent document discovery across massive repositories. This enhances <a href="/blog/ai-customer-support-automation" class="text-primary hover:underline">AI customer support automation</a> by providing instant access to accurate information, and supports <a href="/blog/crm-automation-sales-teams" class="text-primary hover:underline">CRM automation for sales teams</a> with comprehensive product knowledge.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass-morphism p-6 rounded-xl">
                  <div class="bg-primary/20 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path d="M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2M12,4A8,8 0 0,1 20,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,20A8,8 0 0,1 4,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,4M12,6A6,6 0 0,0 6,12A6,6 0 0,0 12,18A6,6 0 0,0 18,12A6,6 0 0,0 12,6Z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-3">Automated Document Classification</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Machine learning algorithms automatically categorize, tag, and organize documents based on content analysis, ensuring consistent classification and compliance adherence.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass-morphism p-6 rounded-xl">
                  <div class="bg-primary/20 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
