                  </div>
                  
                  <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Organizations implementing AI document management systems typically see dramatic improvements in operational efficiency and cost reduction. According to Forrester Research, enterprises achieve an average <strong class="text-primary">312% ROI within 18 months</strong> of implementation, with payback periods averaging 8-12 months.
                  </p>
                  
                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
                    <div class="bg-primary p-6 rounded-xl text-center">
