                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="glass-morphism p-6 rounded-xl">
                      <h4 class="font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-3">Enhanced Decision Making</h4>
                      <p class="text-white text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        AI-powered document analysis provides executives with faster access to critical business information, enabling data-driven decision making with comprehensive context from historical documents and real-time data.
