              <h2 id="implementation-guide" class="text-3xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-8">AI Document Management Implementation Guide</h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="border border-primary p-6 rounded-xl">
                  <h3 class="font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-4">Phase 1: Assessment & Planning (2-4 weeks)</h3>
                  <p class="text-white mb-4">
                    Begin with comprehensive analysis of current document management practices, identifying pain points, volume requirements, and compliance needs. This phase establishes the foundation for successful AI implementation.
                  </p>
                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div>
                      <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Technical Assessment</h4>
                      <ul class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1">
